original: Larsson, Bengt Olof, distriktsveterinär, Borås, f. 18/8/96 i Älgarås, Ska-rab. 1., av Johan L. o. Hilda Andersson. G. 25 m. Ninnan Bokstedt. Barn: Ulla-Britta f. 26, Inga-Lena 28, Anne-Marie 31, Bengt-Olof 38. — Stud:ex. i Örebro 15, veter :ex. 21. Tjg. å stat. vet:med. anst., tf. distr :-vet. i ol. distr., distr :veter. i Varekils distr. 25, i Borås distr. fr. 44. Medl. av Odd Fellow.
translated: Larsson, Bengt Olof, district veterinarian, Borås, b. 18/8/96 in Älgarås, Skaraborg County, son of Johan L. and Hilda Andersson. Married on 25/xx to Ninnan Bokstedt. Children: Ulla-Britta b. 26, Inga-Lena b. 28, Anne-Marie b. 31, Bengt-Olof b. 38. Completed high school in Örebro in 1915, veterinary degree in 1921. Currently working at the state veterinary medical facility as a temporary district veterinarian in several districts, including Varekils district from 1925 and Borås district from 1944. Member of Odd Fellow.
